Using NLP library spacey in python.

You can confirm the image is successfully pulled using the following command  
docker images


Open terminal --> Navigate to the project directory and run the following command to run the docker-compose file
docker compose build
docker compose up

Now open a new terminal and verify if this mongo container is up and running

docker ps

Login to MongoDB with created credentials::

docker exec -it <container-name> bash

mongosh -u admin --authenticationDatabase firstdb


CHART PROTOCOL(Resource Method Chart)
Resource                            Address         Protocol            Parameters                   Response + Statuscode
Register User                       /register       POST                username,pwd - String           200 OK
                                                                                                        301 Invalid username (user already exists!!!)

Detect Similarity of Docs           /detect          POST              username,pwd -String
                                                                            Text1, Text2                200 OK -return similarity of docs
                                                                                                        301 Invalid username 
                                                                                                        302 Invalid pwd
                                                                                                        303 Insufficient tokens
                                                                            
Refill Tokens Sent                  /refill            POST             username,admin_pwd -String      200 OK
                                                                        refill amount                   301 Invalid username
                                                                                                        304 Invalid admin pwd                                                               
                    
                
